The initialization block runs before constructor, This can be used to set the default value when there are multiple constructors
The position of the block is important, 
	Ex1
		String c = "Blue" ;
		
		{
			c= "White";
		}
		//c will be white
		
	Ex2	
		{
			c= "White";
		}
		
		String c = "Blue" ;
		// c will be created with null , then applied the value white and then the default value Blue.
		// c will be Blue
		
		
	